'''Armand Kajangwe''', ni [[Rwanda|umunyarwanda]] - umukinnyi wa firime wo mu Busuwisi . Azwi cyane nk'umuyobozi wa firime nka ''The Asylum'', na ''Dirty Singles'' . 

== Umwuga ==
Ku ya 7 Mata 2009, Kajangwe yinjiye mu isosiyete ikora ibicuruzwa byuzuye yitwa 'Crooked Seas Inc.' yashinzwe na Craig Leblanc ifite icyicaro i Ontario, muri [[Kanada]]. Yakoze nk'umuyobozi, umuyobozi w'amafoto, n'umuyobozi ushinzwe imbuga nkoranyambaga. 

Muri 2016, Kajangwe yagize uruhare mu gutangiza urubuga rwa mbere rwa videwo muri [[Afurika]]. Ihuriro rizwi ku izina rya 'www.journal.rw' ryatunganijwe kandi rikoreshwa na Village Innovation , uruganda ruhanga ruherereye mu [[Rwanda]] aho Kajangwe ari umuyobozi mukuru. Ihuriro rirashobora gutanga inzira yo gusangira ibisobanuro bihanitse bya videwo. 

